metadata.name: Nature's Remembrance 1
metadata.description:
Part of the flow self-portrait series “Nature’s Remembrance”.

"Nature's Remembrance" consists of 12 variations - all unique, all 1/1s - 
each with their own expression, but within the same framework. 

The series was created as a site specific work for my solo exhibition during the performance festival ØKANT in Marstal (DK) 2021. The series was shot inside the factory hall where my exhibition took place, to fulfil the festival prompt of artworks being locally and site specifically anchored.

All initial collectors will be airdropped the poster NF of the 12 variations in the series.
